prediction.sparql:
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?series WHERE {
  ?series wdt:P1346 wd:Q461595 .
  ?series rdfs:label ?seriesLabel
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( ?seriesLabel , "World Series" ) && LANG( ?seriesLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ( GROUP_CONCAT( ?givenNameLabel ; separator = " " ) AS ?fullGivenNames ) ?familyNameLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q312581 wdt:P735 ?givenName .
  ?givenName rdfs:label ?givenNameLabel .
  FILTER ( lang( ?givenNameLabel ) = 'en' ) wd:Q312581 wdt:P734 ?familyName .
  ?familyName rdfs:label ?familyNameLabel .
  FILTER ( lang( ?familyNameLabel ) = 'en' )
}
GROUP BY ?familyNameLabel

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT ?coach WHERE {
  wd:Q330120 p:P286 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P286 ?coach .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?statement pq:P582 ?end .
  }
  FILTER ( ?start <= "2013-12-31T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime ) FILTER ( ! BOUND( ?end ) || ?end >= "2013-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime )
}

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT ?vp WHERE {
  ?vp p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q11699 .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= "2001-01-20T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end >= "1993-01-20T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
SELECT ?actor WHERE {
  wd:Q23831 p:P161 ?castStatement .
  ?castStatement ps:P161 ?actor .
  ?castStatement pq:P453 wd:Q4169030 .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
SELECT ?nbaStart WHERE {
  wd:Q169452 p:P54 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P54 wd:Q161337 ; pq:P580 ?nbaStart .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
SELECT ?statement ?start_time WHERE {
  wd:Q33866 p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q11696 ; pq:P580 ?start_time .
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT ?vp ?vpLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q9696 p:P39 ?presidencyStatement .
  ?presidencyStatement ps:P39 wd:Q11696 ; pq:P580 ?presStart ; pq:P582 ?presEnd .
  ?vp p:P39 ?vpStatement .
  ?vpStatement ps:P39 wd:Q11699 ; pq:P580 ?vpStart ; pq:P582 ?vpEnd .
  FILTER ( ?vpStart <= ?presEnd && ?vpEnd >= ?presStart ) OPTIONAL {
    ?vp rdfs:label ?vpLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?vpLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
SELECT ?actor WHERE {
  ?work p:P161 ?castStatement .
  ?castStatement ps:P161 ?actor .
  ?castStatement pq:P453 wd:Q694790 .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?actor WHERE {
  ?film wdt:P179 wd:Q1102217 .
  ?film wdt:P161 ?actorStatement .
  ?film p:P161 ?castStatement .
  ?castStatement ps:P161 ?actor .
  ?castStatement pq:P453 wd:Q16311 .
}
